{"tid":2454404,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"張致恒老婆雯雯自爆得200蚊要養仔孭起頭家 壓力爆煲冒輕生念頭","createTime":"2021-03-20T08:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T18:06:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":223,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"478c4335a623ea8d79866ffc42f546f0f9ccba68","tid":2454404,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:15:29.000Z","msg":"雯雯今日再在IG貼出跟兒子及婆婆合照，並為放負解畫：「朋友&hellip;&hellip;唔使擔心，我冇事亦都冇癲到，只係最近發生太多事，面對唔到同有爆煲嘅情況。要自己照顧兩個仔同成個屋企，現金只係得$200，所以有啲驚同唔識應對。再加上，有太多我唔知情嘅事情發生，去到我知道嘅時候已經係畀人鬧緊嘅時候，所以開始有啲睇唔開，有自殺嘅念頭，我承認我係有唔成熟同太脆弱。但係當我去到我流眼淚嘅時候，個仔會埋嚟摸吓你，幫你抹走啲眼淚，當我唔開心嘅時候，佢好似明白咁樣，過嚟拍吓你摸吓你嗲吓你。嗰一刻我先醒覺，我唔可以放棄，因為我冇權帶走佢哋嘅生命，嗰一刻我同自己講我一定要堅強，要努力面對一切，先可以陪伴到佢哋去佢哋之後嘅人生。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210320/4KAWML2YSJCFJIJ77UW5IAQGBY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210320%2F4KAWML2YSJCFJIJ77UW5IAQGBY%2F&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=997c3d7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210320%2F4KAWML2YSJCFJIJ77UW5IAQGBY%2F&h=f499eeae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210320/4KAWML2YSJCFJIJ77UW5IAQGBY/</a>"},{"pid":"fa7f045dacf7a94f971df4c94f2b9ea7851f89c7","tid":2454404,"uid":20291,"like":241,"dislike":1,"score":240,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:16:54.000Z","msg":"好快條仔連你都唔要，中出2件幾撚爽"},{"pid":"10099a8236e36601fb7e4d1c2e037c5dc246d580","tid":2454404,"uid":242537,"like":88,"dislike":2,"score":86,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:17:23.000Z","msg":"去建興做囉<br />\n200蚊好多嫁啦<br />\n「一舊水」，英文名Bobo，曾是2000年代中期Sex141經典的一樓一，因當年只收$100服務費，所以被網民命名為「一舊水」。其後廣告改名為「蛇女」、「奇蟹騷」、「奇蟹刀騷」、「神床奇西」等。「一舊水」曾加價至$150，因此有人將她改名為「舊半水」。<br />\n<br />\n「一舊水」亦曾設立中英文兼備的個人網站 (<a href=\"http://xxxx.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fxxxx.hk&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=15d3073c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">xxxx.hk</a>，<a href=\"http://前稱3000hk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%89%8D%E7%A8%B13000hk.com&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=ec89d87d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">前稱3000hk.com</a>)。有高登人曾提出贊助網友幫襯「一舊水」做烈士，迅即獲得數十人支持。"},{"pid":"5a8fc9c4e5ec3f649a500964ae671cbd6aa09ef6","tid":2454404,"uid":38904,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"你唔出去做雞邊個養個仔啊?"},{"pid":"0afcfeed2adb2463f00ed6a38ed386f49440cc73","tid":2454404,"uid":74858,"like":329,"dislike":2,"score":327,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"人無恥真係無敵<br />\n做譚仔阿姐都搵到兩餐啦<br />\n得兩舊水都咁生兩件<br />\n欠債還錢仲怪個債主逼你<br />\n廢人真係廢人死咗都冇人可憐<br />\n個仔有呢d 老豆老母真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71be8e1ce6bd0d2e17adb36cc6fec64f52eebb80","tid":2454404,"uid":18395,"like":148,"dislike":1,"score":147,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:20:40.000Z","msg":"咁撚窮<br />\n又養幾隻狗 同仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90149217b26c7de17dc0076e18ef4b8a92f6e131","tid":2454404,"uid":3063,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:21:34.000Z","msg":"日撚日上網<br />\n話死 話大壓力話呢樣<br />\n無人想知你死唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f53a085ce602c0a0c1b53582c52c9b07ee5c184","tid":2454404,"uid":96743,"like":24,"dislike":8,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:22:08.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n出黎做一定好多人幫襯"},{"pid":"6899a766b687852d7c0ae204f1aab460c474dc4c","tid":2454404,"uid":116143,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:23:15.000Z","msg":"一大堆廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快撚d還錢呀<br />\n成家賤種"},{"pid":"d9e2b743f8e0e9a70c2693e4eeb54643e385b7f3","tid":2454404